Class MovieStatistics

java.lang.Object
com.example.moviepopularitybackend.model.MovieStatistics
public class MovieStatistics extends Object
Represents movie statistics for a specific genre, year, and country. This class encapsulates data about the number of movies produced in a particular genre for a specific year and country.
